title: The Great Reset and the Last Days—Charlie Kirk and Jack Hibbs LIVE from the FUTURES Conference
itunes:title: The Great Reset and the Last Days—Charlie Kirk and Jack Hibbs LIVE from the FUTURES Conference
description:
Charlie joins Pastor Jack Hibbs, live from the Futures Conference at Calvary Chapel Chino Hills for an in depth conversation about The Great Reset and what the Bible has to say about it. In a powerful conversation that has gone viral in the days since this discussion took place, we are honored to bring you the entire unedited conversation here on The Charlie Kirk Show ad free. 

Support the show: http://www.charliekirk.com/support
